manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (com.lingxi.bexplus.ui.bexmain.BexMainActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.

playstore_details.title: Bitcoin Wallet for Margin Trading - Bexplus App
playstore_details.description:
Bexplus app offers opportunities for crypto traders to earn profits through crypto margin trading easily. No KYC and no deposit fee, Bexplus allows you to access futures trading within 30 seconds. You can also store your bitcoins in the interest wallet with up to 30% APR when you are not trading.

You can long or short crypto and make a profit as long as your prediction is right. 100x leverage grants you greater exposure and increases your profitability.

Step 1: Deposit bitcoin worth higher than $10 (buy bitcoin on Bexplus if you don’t have it yet).
Step 2: Choose a trading pair among BTC, ETH, LTC, EOS, and XPR.
Step 3: Make your prediction and select "BUY/UP" or "SELL/DOWN".
Step 4: If the price of the trading pair goes up or down as you predict, you will make a profit.
Furthermore, with the 100x leverage toll, you can invest only 0.01 BTC to hold a 1 BTC position. If the price goes up or down by 1%, it becomes 100% for you and your investment will be doubled!

Key Features:
■ High profitability - 100x leverage to 100x the earning
■ Trading pairs: BTC, ETH, LTC, EOS, XPR 
■ Trading simulator - A 10-BTC funded demo account to learn how to trade and practice strategies
■ Languages - English, Spanish, and 13 other languages. With the Bexplus mobile crypto trading app, you can go long or short on Bitcoin or any other cryptocurrencies to make profits no matter in the bull market or bear market. Bexplus offers crypto derivative trading on Bitcoin(BTC), Ethereum(ETH), Litecoin(LTC), EOS, and Ripple (XRP). 

Still a beginner? Bexplus offers free trial Bitcoins to help you get familiar with the trading platform and learn how to make profits with evens or odds. You can also purchase your first bitcoin on the Bexplus app.

Already an expert? Come try the most easy-handled Bitcoin trading tool in the market! With Bexplus tools, you can watch the market K-line in real-time, make a judgment quickly, place orders effectively, and collect margins collectively.

** Why Bexplus App is Your Must Choice **
📈 Real-Time Quotes on Stable Charts: Professional K-line trends of various indicators are provided on real-time charts. You can choose a variety of indicators to predict market trends of Bitcoin, ETH, Litecoin, EOS, and XRP. 
🔒 Security Guaranteed Safety is our primary concern. Bexplus offers protection against DDoS attacks and is encrypted with SSL, multi-signature technology, 2FA to secure users' accounts and assets.
💰 Trade Easily Bexplus: We provide a convenient interface for you to access cryptocurrency futures trading. Signing up takes less than 30 seconds and requires no personal information. Deposit only requires 1 block confirmation.
🛠️ Diversified Trading Modes: You can also make profits by longing or shorting when there are small price fluctuations. Amplify gains by leveraging transactions, which help maximize profits. Set take-profit or stop-loss points to lower risks.
⏲️ High Liquidity Extra-fast orders execution even during great market fluctuations, no spread, and with low latency. 
🏦Interest-bearing Wallet: Safely store Bitcoin and enjoy up to 30% annualized interest. Instant deposit and withdrawal, and 24/7 available. 
🙋‍♀️ 24/7 Customer Support: Having issues? Feel free to send an email to support@bexplus.com. A 100% Deposit Bonus and New Users Get Free Dogecoin promotion are running. Download the Bexplus app now!
Official: https://www.bexplus.com/
